503
00:45:36,275 --> 00:45:37,276
Why you…

504
00:45:38,903 --> 00:45:40,655
-I did my best.
-Are you a foreigner?

505
00:45:40,738 --> 00:45:42,949
Are you not from here?
Are you from the States?

506
00:45:44,784 --> 00:45:47,411
Get your guard up. Do it, you brat.

507
00:45:47,495 --> 00:45:49,080
Keep your guard up, you punk.

508
00:45:55,294 --> 00:45:57,713
Please save me. She's going to kill me.

509
00:45:57,797 --> 00:46:00,007
You don't deserve to be saved.

