Gosh, my mirror.

765
01:05:37,934 --> 01:05:38,810
Sorry.

766
01:05:38,893 --> 01:05:42,188
I closed the curtains for a reason.

767
01:05:43,106 --> 01:05:45,942
All right. So is everyone here?

768
01:05:54,784 --> 01:05:58,163
As tenants, we want your promise.

769
01:06:00,039 --> 01:06:03,042
That's why we plan to draw up
an agreement by tomorrow.

770
01:06:03,626 --> 01:06:05,587
And you can sign it
by the end of this week.

771
01:06:05,670 --> 01:06:08,798
I know what you said yesterday,
but are you really a lawyer in Italy?

772
01:06:10,383 --> 01:06:11,217
Yes.

773
01:06:11,301 --> 01:06:14,053
Then how will you handle it
when you don't know our law?

774
01:06:14,137 --> 01:06:16,806
I don't think
my legal qualification matters here.

775
01:06:16,890 --> 01:06:18,808
Our promise to you and your signatures do.

776
01:06:18,892 --> 01:06:22,395
I will guarantee that you will have
your lots back once I rebuild this place.

777
01:06:22,478 --> 01:06:23,563
You promise, right?

778
01:06:25,690 --> 01:06:27,901
We never lie.

779
01:06:27,984 --> 01:06:29,360
What do you think?

780
01:06:30,111 --> 01:06:34,574
Well, they seem very genuine.
Why don't we trust them?

781
01:06:34,657 --> 01:06:39,913
I'm also going to trust you,
Mr. Vincenzo Casanova.

782
01:06:40,455 --> 01:06:42,749
Yes. Me, too, Mr. Casanova.

783
01:06:46,085 --> 01:06:47,670
Let me inform you in advance.

784
01:06:51,841 --> 01:06:53,468
I know martial arts.

785
01:06:54,260 --> 01:06:56,721
If you are deceiving us,

786
01:06:56,804 --> 01:07:00,850
I'm going to put you in a guillotine choke
for six days straight.

787
01:07:01,476 --> 01:07:05,146
Don't do stuff like that. No one cares.
You're embarrassing and so tacky.

788
01:07:05,230 --> 01:07:06,648
Let's sum it up.

789
01:07:07,482 --> 01:07:09,025
Who agrees to trust them?

790
01:07:12,070 --> 01:07:16,115
My gosh. That annoying Vincenzo.
This doesn't feel right.

791
01:07:16,950 --> 01:07:18,743
We have no choice.

792
01:07:19,369 --> 01:07:21,120
Right. Damn it.

793
01:07:21,204 --> 01:07:24,207
This is driving me crazy. Darn it.

794
01:07:24,290 --> 01:07:27,043
Let's give him the benefit of the doubt
and go with the flow.

795
01:07:34,717 --> 01:07:36,052
Merciful Buddha.

796
01:07:47,730 --> 01:07:48,773
Mr. Hong.

797
01:07:48,856 --> 01:07:51,776
The tenants have nothing
but your word to go on.

798
01:07:53,194 --> 01:07:54,737
But I find this unfortunate

799
01:07:55,363 --> 01:07:57,448
because it looks like
you're toying with us.

800
01:07:59,867 --> 01:08:02,161
Is it that hard for you to trust me?

801
01:08:03,580 --> 01:08:07,417
I pretended to trust you earlier
to assure the other tenants,

802
01:08:09,043 --> 01:08:12,797
but I never trust people like you.

803
01:08:20,054 --> 01:08:21,472
I am a lawyer,

804
01:08:21,556 --> 01:08:23,683
and so are you.

805
01:08:25,226 --> 01:08:26,853
But we clearly have different jobs.

806
01:08:27,854 --> 01:08:29,480
You represent money,

807
01:08:29,564 --> 01:08:31,274
but I represent people.

808
01:08:35,737 --> 01:08:38,031
I also represent people.

809
01:08:38,114 --> 01:08:39,365
Oh, yes.

810
01:08:40,033 --> 01:08:41,451
Rich people.

811
01:08:43,161 --> 01:08:47,206
I know Babel E&C will buy this building
so I prepared myself for everything.

812
01:08:47,290 --> 01:08:49,542
So don't pretend
to be a mediator in front of me.

813
01:08:49,626 --> 01:08:51,461
Just proceed with your plan.

814
01:09:16,319 --> 01:09:17,403
Where's everyone?

815
01:09:19,072 --> 01:09:19,989
Honey.

816
01:09:20,615 --> 01:09:21,741
Ju-yeong.

817
01:09:22,325 --> 01:09:23,451
My goodness!

818
01:09:23,993 --> 01:09:25,203
Honey!

819
01:09:25,286 --> 01:09:26,287
Ju-yeong!

820
01:09:27,205 --> 01:09:29,707
-Who are you people?
-We don't have time to chitchat.

821
01:09:33,461 --> 01:09:34,545
Ju-yeong.

822
01:09:40,760 --> 01:09:43,304
GEUMGA PLAZA CONTRACT OF SALES

823
01:09:43,388 --> 01:09:44,764
-All right.
-You…

824
01:09:45,932 --> 01:09:47,225
Stamp your seal on it.

825
01:09:48,643 --> 01:09:50,436
I have a show to catch on TV.

826
01:10:07,412 --> 01:10:08,579
ATTORNEY HONG CHA-YOUNG

827
01:10:08,663 --> 01:10:10,331
JIPURAGI LAW FIRM, LAWYER HONG YU-CHAN

828
01:10:10,415 --> 01:10:11,874
RECIPIENT HONG CHA-YOUNG

829
01:10:12,667 --> 01:10:14,752
